WEBVTT

00:07.549 --> 00:08.818
Why didn't he just tell me

00:08.853 --> 00:09.984
he was changing?

00:10.019 --> 00:12.772
He didn't want anyone
to know.

00:12.807 --> 00:15.525
And I promised him
no one would.

00:17.000 --> 00:23.074
